    "body": "I personally feel like pwsh shouldnâ€™t be ordering at all and just output the objects as they are retrieved from the file system. This is more performant when dealing with large structures as it doesnâ€™t need to collect everything to then sort. If the end user desires it to be sorted they can pipe the output into `Sort-Object` and sort as they wish.",
